description: A simple C# toolbox repository holding together useful functions.
releaseNotes:
2.1.0 

Added DisposableEnumerator class for handling an enumeration of IDisposable objects so that it can used in a using statement or via a single Dispose method. Does not run internal enumeration until it runs itself.

Additionally I have moved a couple of extension classes to the Collections namespace (keeping temporary references for now to ensure compatibility)

2.0.0 

A total stripped down version from v1 in that Lski.Toobox.Data, Lski.Toolbox.Drawing and System.Linq.Dynamic have been removed

These are now available in seperate packages. Please see project site for more information
